## **1. Command Type Determination**

Decide what to do with each command:

```c
if (is_builtin(cmd->args[0]))
    execute_builtin(cmd);      // Run in parent process
else if (is_external(cmd->args[0]))
    execute_external(cmd);     // Fork + execve
else
    error("command not found");
```

